Hi, I finished deploy.
In this url (http://52.8.237.119/items/spiders/amazon/) you can see results of crawling.
To run new task you should execute the next command in the terminal:
curl http://52.8.237.119:80/schedule.json -d project=spiders -d spider=amazon -d searchterms_str=laptop -d page=1

Where searchterms_str may be some search keyword and page - quantity of required pages.

To directly send request from URL
http://52.8.237.119:5000/add_task?searchterms_str=laptop+hp&page=1

Where searchterms_str is keyword and page - quantity of pages.
